                Belize should use more 
                <input type="text" id="q_c_1" class="inline-input" placeholder="energy source"> 
                energy because 
                <input type="text" id="q_c_1_reason" class="inline-input" placeholder="reason">.
                <br>
                <em>(Note: The first blank and reason are graded together as one item worth 2 marks based on keywords).</em>
